        <li> <p id = descriptionLongue> The Visual Reflex Test consists of measuring the time it takes for the patient to react to a stimulus in his environment. This test will be carried out using our module developed for this project: the patient will have in each hand a remote control consisting of a button and a multicoloured LED. The aim is to press the button of the corresponding control as quickly as possible when a button lights up. The test time is estimated at 2 min30. </p></li>
